1, 2. Yehova asaka vatu vatwame ngachilihi mujitanga? YEHOVA KALUNGA ikiye ahakileko ulo wakulivanga. Mbimbiliya yatulweza ngwayo Kalunga atengele pwevo wakulivanga, kaha ‘amunehele kuli lunga.’ Alama awahililile chikuma nakwamba ngwenyi: “Ou napu jino chifuwa chakuvifuwa vyami, nyama yakunyama yami.” (Kuputuka 2:22, 23) Echi chasolola nge Yehova asaka vatu vaze valimbata vapwenga vakuwahilila. 2 Chaluvinda, vatu vavavulu kavapwa vakuwahilila mujitanga javoko. Oloze muMbimbiliya mwatwama jindong
